[normal]&#xa0;[bold]&#xa0;[bold]      Customer Experience[bold]4.4
[normal]&#xa0; 
[normal]British Airways is investing £18 million in improving its customers’ experience during disruption. Over the next 12 months the airline’s new ‘Disruption Management Programme’ will provide the right tools, technologies, trai
[normal]ning and processes so that British Airways can continue to deliver outstanding service to its customers, even in times of disruption.
[normal] 
[normal]British Airways has improved how it manages its customers’ journeys when they have been disrupted with the following measu
[normal]res:
